{"tid":1283650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港要統領廣東，先可以同中共搏鬥，呢個先係長遠既下一步","createTime":"2019-07-04T01:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:04:52.000Z","uid":260704,"like":54,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa38240886711387020f0fa56df49a8457bd1599","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"其實大家都好清楚，目前癱瘓左立法會到十月<br />\n<br />\n目前黎計我地換來幾個月時間黎思考下一場民眾運動應該點行（除非有新既佔領目標而係有意義）<br />\n<br />\n但有無諗過，呢幾個月係和理非製造輿論去反滲透番<br />\n<br />\n廣東/大陸既人，諗辦法係中共體制內掀起更大既革命呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n其實據大家所認識，由最近廣州曾經捍衛廣東話、茉莉花革命<br />\n<br />\n愈遠既會有臺灣、新疆、西藏、蒙古。<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎，佢地既抗爭都比我地行得更前<br />\n<br />\n但佢地做十次先有我地做一次國際同等關注程度既效果<br />\n<br />\n係因為佢地俾人滅聲得大勁，而臺灣自身又好撚唔爭氣<br />\n<br />\n而香港係國際關係上又處於一個蝴蝶效應生態，國際對於<br />\n<br />\n香港既取態其實咪又係虎視眈眈，從香港既缺口可以令中<br />\n<br />\n共逃避，或者透過香港來轉化，自從中国成為第二大經濟<br />\n<br />\n體就不嬲令大把國家以利益行先，但永遠後知後覺所帶來<br />\n<br />\n既破壞係更大，依家出面成班人想斬佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換一個講法，而且係無可奈何既講法，香港同周邊地區有<br />\n<br />\n命運共同體既宿命，我地必需攞番主導權，長遠黎講<br />\n<br />\n南北戰爭既意識形態在所難免，歷史一定會係重覆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：p牌、臺灣國番黎、9/6-1/7前線成員"},{"pid":"536e616f3a0b3bdd934aa066686631ee99512869","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c83980af76be9d643d6d96cb12885ca88160afa4","tid":1283650,"uid":258770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"正確<br />\n但要做一兩年文宣先 大陸毫無反抗意識<br />\n佢地覺得錢就係一切 中國係最強既國家<br />\n要搵到位入說服佢反抗地先"},{"pid":"b3468a5261116c8858a73957cef79774812d79bf","tid":1283650,"uid":161322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:24:28.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <br />\n我要搵律師 (冇電話就問佢拎律師聯絡冊)<br />\n我要通知家人朋友<br />\n我唔簽任何文件<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要食飯 飲水 拎毛氈 去廁所<br />\n我唔舒服想去醫院<br />\n我要向值日官投訴"},{"pid":"cd1819a6f540b424c6ad3f2a2ac96e9a09304f21","tid":1283650,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=======================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家記得善用Blockchain 永久backup重要個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【網絡安全】如何匿名免費咁放資料上Ethereum Blockchain測試網絡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282498</a></span>"},{"pid":"9c8079b7350f09fd79fe2ea141c98e1c2ef26c74","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c83980af76be9d643d6d96cb12885ca88160afa4","tid":1283650,"uid":258770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"正確<br />\n但要做一兩年文宣先 大陸毫無反抗意識<br />\n佢地覺得錢就係一切 中國係最強既國家<br />\n要搵到位入說服佢反抗地先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"呢個都可能係我地香港人見到表面果層<br />\n<br />\n一定有部分廣東、西藏、新疆人，維吾爾族人同我地有一樣諗法<br />\n<br />\n一個多民族國家，尤其極權統治，正如羅馬隔離都有佛羅<br />\n<br />\n倫斯，香港人眼看世界格局要夠闊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n革命既意識最重要係要俾佢萌芽<br />\n<br />\n正如種植物咁，種子轉化都要特別處理啦"},{"pid":"32d2164bc618a89bd6b59b80bce54c07b1f6e45a","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd1819a6f540b424c6ad3f2a2ac96e9a09304f21","tid":1283650,"uid":159913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=======================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家記得善用Blockchain 永久backup重要個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【網絡安全】如何匿名免費咁放資料上Ethereum Blockchain測試網絡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282498</a></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"你諗少左"},{"pid":"74b9497f7c6d7acc88e81ad0c5e313337f2699b2","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7d6569a7883861de513f34b7931dd5fe166fa5d","tid":1283650,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:54:52.000Z","msg":"天窗理論"},{"pid":"6214eff750fa42253d067eed163a42ee692c14de","tid":1283650,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"中國人性情是總喜歡調和、折中的。<br />\n譬如你說，這屋子太暗，須在這裡開一個窗，大家一定不允許的。<br />\n但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。<br />\n沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。<br />\n――魯迅 &middot;《無聲的中國》"},{"pid":"753d076b092fa3cd2324c5a1445c1f2508c12ea1","tid":1283650,"uid":261852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:01:59.000Z","msg":"自動送頭大媽區?"},{"pid":"16c226fd880b138186089c1d76dbfde53c9eb993","tid":1283650,"uid":30290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"其實大陸都好多人不滿中共。之前 d 騷動少極都成千人。不過怕武力打壓所以唔出黎既人佔好多，所以有心冇力係大陸人d 騷亂搞唔大既原因。正因為咁，其實其唔可行。令中共解體既方法一係外國開戰二係內部分裂，重點唔係市民而係由幹部開始咁先有機"},{"pid":"91845130794d00d7562af4c6d7d833c30df427fa","tid":1283650,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"廣州獨立"},{"pid":"bc1e8a9d5c074f85604775cb7a6b264832340696","tid":1283650,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"港獨個班都唔撐你啦要乜廣東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa7004e683cca7c5f5c3b44d6b853d8fc72edaa","tid":1283650,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P牌仔</span></span>"},{"pid":"4b26c31e782e99b6692db28c8c770549141853fe","tid":1283650,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"P牌仔<br />\n<br />\n我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"c635266399661b97a75e4843da4b1795c1d67802","tid":1283650,"uid":237747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a31a7b29ebd9ddb7a8c5d40c8b60d6abc39d3a01","tid":1283650,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fa7004e683cca7c5f5c3b44d6b853d8fc72edaa","tid":1283650,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P牌仔</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:55:58.000Z","msg":"#15呢位user一早block左"},{"pid":"1367279174fb87910f302d7b82578b1fd22f066f","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"753d076b092fa3cd2324c5a1445c1f2508c12ea1","tid":1283650,"uid":261852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:01:59.000Z","msg":"自動送頭大媽區?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"唔係 係輸出革命"},{"pid":"2f2a840b9b53e4239b756b1bc5aacde658477433","tid":1283650,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"249f30afeb455cae50459bbd22a5c578db5501bc","tid":1283650,"uid":260704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"2a2d076c3a72abbbbe7aaa67f2e70b3976f4f1c3","tid":1283650,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa160bf6ee7fdb53251ac3f53dbbccd8ec56841","tid":1283650,"uid":4419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38647710199bd098ec33a52bb5c1b158fe912f93","tid":1283650,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884e65f5a92f0ad56bb9c67fcc8ee1673dd2632f","tid":1283650,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:56:11.000Z","msg":"統你老母，係都要將香港同埋d垃圾地方撈埋一齊，咩居心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港就係香港，唔理民主定獨立建國，都冇需要拉埋其他地方一齊！大中華膠大廣東膠唔好乘機洗人腦"}]}